          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"header4\" group=\"Headers\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n                    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Subtitle\" name=\"showSubTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Media Size\" name=\"mediaSize\" min=\"30\" max=\"100\" step=\"5\" value=\"45\">\n\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Background Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background1-1.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" value=\"#000000\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Background Video\" value=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=36YgDDJ7XSc\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#232323\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-md-center\">\n            <div class=\"media-content col-lg-10 col-md-7\">\n                <div class=\"mbr-figure\">\n                    <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/00073e2a-3042-4589-869b-c648c3acac9e.png\" alt=\"2026 Sage Delio Portrait\" title>\n                </div>\n                <h1 class=\"mbr-section-title align-center mbr-black pb-3 mbr-bold mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">\"I\"</h1>\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle align-center mbr-black mbr-light pb-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showSubTitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet</h3>\n                <div class=\"mbr-text align-center mbr-white\">\n                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-black mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\"><b>| BIOGRAPHY |<br></b>Sage Delio (née Fremont) is an award-winning visual artist, creative technologist, <a href=\"https://sagedelio.com/music\" class=\"text-info\">musician</a>, <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/stores/Sage-Delio/author/B0B1THDYMC\" class=\"text-info\" target=\"_blank\">writer</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.imdb.com/name/nm12033732/\" class=\"text-info\" target=\"_blank\">voice actor</a> based in the Greater Philadelphia Area. Her work explores psychosis, neuroscience, and the shifting architecture of perception, drawing from lived experiences with schizophrenia, autism, and the neurological effects of dopamine and antipsychotic medication.<br><br>Trained in computer science and information technology, Delio’s practice is grounded in both technical rigor and conceptual experimentation. She moves fluidly between code and art to construct immersive systems that merge geometric abstraction, sound, and narrative—translating complex internal states into shared, experiential forms.<br><br>Her multidisciplinary work spans visual art, music, film &amp; video, poetry, and vocal performance. As a visual artist, she is known for surreal and structurally driven compositions. Her writing blends confessional and experimental modes, often integrating elements of science, perception, and technological language. She is the author of <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Blue-Confessional-Poetry-Sage-Delio/dp/B09ZCSVXK5\" class=\"text-info\" target=\"_blank\"><i>Blue Confessional</i></a>, a collection of poetry and prose, and serves as Editor-in-Chief of <a href=\"https://gabbyandmin.com/current-issue\" class=\"text-info\" target=\"_blank\"><i>Gabby &amp; Min’s Literary Review</i></a>.<br><br>Her music ranges from classical and folk influences to experimental and electronic forms, released under Sage Delio as well as the projects <a href=\"https://merryonette.com\" class=\"text-info\" target=\"_blank\"><i>Merry Onette</i></a>, <a href=\"https://aprilomen.com\" class=\"text-info\" target=\"_blank\"><i>April Omen</i></a>, <a href=\"https://siphonrecords.bandcamp.com/\" class=\"text-info\" target=\"_blank\"><i>Gibson Heights</i></a>, and <a href=\"https://summimors.bandcamp.com/\" class=\"text-info\" target=\"_blank\"><i>Summi Mors</i></a>. As a voice actor, her work extends into character and narrative performance, further expanding her exploration of identity, tone, and embodied expression across mediums. Across all disciplines, her work constructs environments where distortion, rhythm, and structure function as a language of their own.<br><br>In addition to her artistic practice, Delio is a <a href=\"https://sagefremont.com/\" class=\"text-info\" target=\"_blank\">computer scientist</a>, software engineer, and <a href=\"https://www.bflatinteractive.com/about\" class=\"text-info\" target=\"_blank\">video game developer</a>. Her space simulation project <a href=\"https://bflatinteractive.itch.io/return-to-nothing\" class=\"text-info\" target=\"_blank\"><i>Return to Nothing</i></a> placed in the top 8% for Innovation at Ludum Dare 45.<br><br>She is the founder and CEO of <a href=\"https://delioenterprises.com/\" class=\"text-info\" target=\"_blank\">Delio Enterprises</a>, overseeing ventures including <a href=\"https://siphonrecords.com\" class=\"text-info\" target=\"_blank\">Siphon Records</a>, <a href=\"https://bflatinteractive.com\" class=\"text-info\" target=\"_blank\">BFlat Interactive</a>, and <a href=\"https://gabbyandmin.com\" class=\"text-info\" target=\"_blank\">Gabby &amp; Min Publications</a>. Her work has been recognized through multiple exhibitions and awards, noted for both its imaginative scope and technical precision.<br><br><b>| EXHIBITIONS |</b><br>2026 The Virtuosity of Play, Restive Moves Multimedia Festival, UC Irvine (Irvine, CA)<br>2022 Ludum Dare 51 (Online)<br>2021 Artist Choice VI Exhibition, Camelback Gallery (Scottsdale, AZ)<br>2021 “Abstracts” Art Exhibition, LST Gallery (Palm Springs, CA)<br>2021 “CityScapes” Art Exhibition, LST Gallery (Palm Springs, CA)<br>2020 Ludum Dare 46 (Online)<br>2019 Ludum Dare 45 (Online)<br><br><b>| AWARDS |</b><br>2021: Silver Award,&nbsp;Camelback Gallery — <i>Woman in Dress</i><br>2021: Special Recognition Award, LST Gallery — <i>Transcendence</i><br>2021: Special Recognition Award, LST Gallery — <i>City of Smog</i><br>2020: Top 3% in the \"Theme\" category at Ludum Dare 46 — <a href=\"https://bflatinteractive.itch.io/vital-2020-windows\" class=\"text-info\" target=\"_blank\" style><i>VITAL 2020</i></a><b style><br></b>2019: Top 8% for \"Innovation\" at Ludum Dare 45 — <a href=\"https://bflatinteractive.itch.io/return-to-nothing\" class=\"text-info\" target=\"_blank\" style><i>Return To Nothing</i></a><br><br><br></p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"mbr-section-btn pt-3 align-center\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\"><a class=\"btn btn-md btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobirise.co\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">View More</a></div>\n            </div>\n\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
